Hey, d'you know where
Queen Lagert's palace is?

rows.label: tlk43200144_03_msg0002

right here, duh! Oh, but regular
folks aren't allowed inside.

windows, hoping I might steal a
peek at the Queen, but no dice.

rows.label: tlk43200144_03_msg0004
rows.name: Actually, I've not seen anyone at all!

rows.label: tlk43200144_03_msg0005

Nobles of the six houses of
Invidia are all soooo private...
